Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ハーモニー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:36.91,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}突然に生まれる
